## Project Timeline (8 Weeks)

| Weeks | Phase | Focus |
|---|---|---|
| 1–2 | Diagnostics | Tile failure analysis on GPT-2 layers; identify worst-case hardware effects |
| 3–4 | Math & Code | Define multi-objective loss; modify SpinQuant optimization loop for AIMC loss |
| 5–6 | Optimization | Run rotation search; visualize pre/post distributions and tile outputs |
| 7 | Benchmarking | Full model inference via AIHWKit; baseline vs SpinQuant vs our rotation |
| 8 | Report | Quantify HAT bypass potential; recommendations for AIMC-aware model design |

