## Where to Start for Common Tasks

| Task | Look here |
|---|---|
| Understand rotation math | `src/rotation_utils.py` |
| Add a new rotation type | `src/rotation_utils.py`, then wire into `1layertests/explore_rotations.py` |
| Define a new hardware loss | `src/loss.py` (create if absent) |
| Implement rotation optimizer | `src/optimizer.py` (create if absent), modeled on SpinQuant's `optimize_rotation.py` |
| Change analog HW configs | `1layertests/explore_rotations.py` (RPU configs inline, move to `src/` when reused) |
| Full GPT-2 pipeline | `src/baseline_forward.py` → `src/apply_rotation.py` |
| Visualize results | `1layertests/plot_results.py` |
| Rebuild the environment | `aimc-docker/Dockerfile` |
| Reference SpinQuant | https://github.com/facebookresearch/SpinQuant |
